## Event System (BroadcastReceiver)

### Emit event
```typescript
import { ON_CARD_MATCHED } from '../data/GameEvents';

// Emit bằng cc.director
cc.director.emit(ON_CARD_MATCHED, { cardId, pairId });
```

### Listen event
```typescript
import { ON_CARD_MATCHED } from '../data/GameEvents';

// Trong onLoad() hoặc start()
cc.director.on(ON_CARD_MATCHED, this._onCardMatched, this);

// Trong onDestroy() — luôn remove để tránh memory leak
cc.director.off(ON_CARD_MATCHED, this._onCardMatched, this);

private onCardMatched(data: { cardId: string; pairId: string }): void {
  // xử lý
}
```

> **Luôn** remove listener trong `onDestroy()` để tránh memory leak.

